\section{Requirements}The requirements for the function, F9 : $x^y$ are given below : \\
\subsection{1:} Calculator should take two inputs which are 'x' and 'y'.
\subsection{2:} Calculator has to check input type and if it is not numberical then it will give and error.
\subsection{3:} Calculator should take only real numbers as input.
